      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>LYF 新疆葵花籽 30g 小包装</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n        background-color: #fdf6ec;\n        color: #333;\n    }\n    header {\n        background-color: #d32f2f;\n        color: white;\n        padding: 10px 20px;\n        text-align: center;\n        font-size: 1.4em;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n    .container {\n        max-width: 1200px;\n        margin: auto;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n    .product-section {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        background: white;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    .product-img {\n        flex: 1;\n        min-width: 300px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .product-img img {\n        max-width: 100%;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    .product-details {\n        flex: 2;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n    .product-title {\n        font-size: 1.8em;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        color: #d32f2f;\n    }\n    .product-brand {\n        color: #888;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    .price {\n        margin: 20px 0;\n        font-size: 1.4em;\n    }\n    .price .current {\n        color: #e65100;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        margin-right: 10px;\n    }\n    .price .original {\n        text-decoration: line-through;\n        color: #999;\n    }\n    .promo-tag {\n        display: inline-block;\n        background-color: #ff9800;\n        color: white;\n        padding: 5px 10px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        font-size: 0.9em;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n    }\n    .stock {\n        margin-top: 10px;\n        color: #388e3c;\n    }\n    .buy-module {\n        margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n    .buy-module input {\n        width: 50px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .btn {\n        padding: 10px 20px;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        font-size: 1em;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        margin: 5px;\n    }\n    .btn-buy {\n        background-color: #d32f2f;\n        color: white;\n    }\n    .btn-cart {\n        background-color: #ff9800;\n        color: white;\n    }\n    .btn:hover {\n        opacity: 0.9;\n    }\n    .recommend-section {\n        margin-top: 30px;\n        background: white;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    .recommend-list {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .recommend-item {\n        flex: 1 1 200px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .recommend-item img {\n        max-width: 100%;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    .recommend-item p {\n        margin: 5px 0;\n    }\n    .comments-section {\n        margin-top: 30px;\n        background: white;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    .comment {\n        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n        padding: 10px 0;\n    }\n    .comment:last-child {\n        border-bottom: none;\n    }\n    .rating {\n        color: #ffa000;\n    }\n    footer {\n        background-color: #d32f2f;\n        color: white;\n        text-align: center;\n        padding: 10px;\n        margin-top: 30px;\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n        .product-section {\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .product-details {\n            padding: 10px;\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<header>春节特惠！LYF新疆葵花籽 30g 小包装</header>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"product-section\">\n        <div class=\"product-img\">\n            <img src=\"sunflower.jpg\" alt=\"LYF 新疆葵花籽\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"product-details\">\n            <div class=\"product-title\">LYF 新疆葵花籽 30g 小包装</div>\n            <div class=\"product-brand\">品牌：LYF</div>\n            <div class=\"product-desc\">精选新疆优质葵花籽，颗粒饱满，香脆可口，独立小包装，方便携带，春节走亲访友必备零食。</div>\n            <div class=\"price\">\n                <span class=\"current\">￥16.9 / 10包</span>\n                <span class=\"original\">￥25.9</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"promo-tag\">限时抢购</div>\n            <div class=\"stock\">库存充足，快来抢购！</div>\n            <div class=\"buy-module\">\n                数量：\n                <button onclick=\"changeQty(-1)\">-</button>\n                <input type=\"number\" id=\"qty\" value=\"1\" min=\"1\" onchange=\"updateTotal()\">\n                <button onclick=\"changeQty(1)\">+</button>\n                <div>单件价格：￥16.9</div>\n                <div id=\"total-price\">总价：￥16.9</div>\n                <div id=\"delivery-info\">预计送达：3-5天</div>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-cart\" onclick=\"addToCart()\">加入购物车</button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-buy\" onclick=\"buyNow()\">立即购买</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"recommend-section\">\n        <h2>为您推荐</h2>\n        <div class=\"recommend-list\">\n            <div class=\"recommend-item\">\n                <img src=\"nut.jpg\" alt=\"新疆核桃\">\n                <p>新疆核桃 200g</p>\n                <p>￥29.9</p>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-buy\">购买</button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"recommend-item\">\n                <img src=\"almond.jpg\" alt=\"巴旦木\">\n                <p>巴旦木 150g</p>\n                <p>￥19.9</p>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-buy\">购买</button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"recommend-item\">\n                <img src=\"pumpkin.jpg\" alt=\"南瓜籽\">\n                <p>南瓜籽 100g</p>\n                <p>￥15.9</p>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-buy\">购买</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"comments-section\">\n        <h2>用户评论</h2>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <div class=\"rating\">★★★★★</div>\n            <p>葵花籽特别香，包装精美，春节送礼很合适！</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <div class=\"rating\">★★★★</div>\n            <p>味道很好，就是快递稍微慢了一点。</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<footer>\n    © 2024 LYF 零食旗舰店 | 支持支付宝、微信支付 | 物流：顺丰速运\n</footer>\n\n<script>\n    function changeQty(change) {\n        let qtyInput = document.getElementById('qty');\n        let qty = parseInt(qtyInput.value) + change;\n        if (qty < 1) qty = 1;\n        qtyInput.value = qty;\n        updateTotal();\n    }\n    function updateTotal() {\n        let qty = parseInt(document.getElementById('qty').value);\n        let total = (qty * 16.9).toFixed(2);\n        document.getElementById('total-price').innerText = '总价：￥' + total;\n    }\n    function addToCart() {\n        alert('已加入购物车！');\n    }\n    function buyNow() {\n        alert('跳转到支付页面...');\n    }\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
